{"TopicId":11832,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"I hope KSP looks like this one day (screens from Space Engine)","CreatedByName":"Baleur","CreatedById":9954,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T15:37:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Baleur","CreatedById":9954,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T15:37:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.spikednation.com/sites/default/files/emvideo-youtube-k8a0Kr2CLQo.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022emvideo-youtube-k8a0Kr2CLQo.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.trickslanka.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/SpaceEngine.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022SpaceEngine.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://jwa.org/system/files/mediaobjects/space_engine_planets_and_galaxies-cc.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022space_engine_planets_and_galaxies-cc.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://meta.filesmelt.com/downloader.php?file=scr00001.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022downloader.php?file=scr00001.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i53.tinypic.com/vqmjyx.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022vqmjyx.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/4/14094969.jpg\u0022 alt=\u002214094969.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/4/401231068.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022401231068.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/4/577054453.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022577054453.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/4/973925512.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022973925512.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/4/566918808.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022566918808.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/2/446307250.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022446307250.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/2/811572866.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022811572866.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/2/555295101.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022555295101.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/2/616821066.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022616821066.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/2/627534377.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022627534377.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/2/263156330.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022263156330.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/5/947109099.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022947109099.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/5/748570188.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022748570188.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/5/507335448.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022507335448.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/5/702081819.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022702081819.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/5/443447390.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022443447390.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/3/810206377.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022810206377.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/_ph/3/591823074.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022591823074.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENo joke, this is realtime. And it actually runs good too, at speeds of KSP rockets it runs at 60fps even on 0 planet detail (the setting 0 is considered high, with negative values considered lower). Which is still far beyond the quality of many movies and Star Trek / Stargate episodes.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKSP with similar achievements in the visual department would be my dream game of all time, no question. Not to mention the procedural galaxies (yes plural), infinite exploration potential.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPerhaps not this iteration of KSP, but maybe a sequel or \u0027three-quel?\u0027 in the future.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe russians sure know how to code..\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://en.spaceengine.org/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://en.spaceengine.org/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frostiken","CreatedById":1837,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T15:38:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EUnfortunately all SpaceEngine ever looks like to me is a stream of errors flying across the screen and then a catastrophic crash to desktop.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Baleur","CreatedById":9954,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T15:41:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIndeed, if moving at lightspeed. But moving at KSP rocket speeds it\\\u0027s fine.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdFire75","CreatedById":18964,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T15:46:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ETo be honest, I hope it stay quite cartoony, It suits the game very well.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ted","CreatedById":26298,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T15:57:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhile I think SpaceEngine is amazing and is a lot of fun to relax with, KSP shouldn\\\u0027t look like that.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKSP has a very stylised look to it, if it was to look like that then there would be an expectation for the rest of the design to be ultra-realistic.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHowever, the mechanics of SpaceEngine (procedural generation etc) should definitely be considered in KSP.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThinking more about it though, if KSP managed to retain its current style while still looking more aesthetically pleasing, that would would be awesome.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}